name: Iperf3-Cygwin-GUI
short_description:
GUI frontend for Iperf3. Iperf3-Cygwin-GUI is a network performance test tool with graphical user interface.

Iperf is a popular network performance test tool. The homepage of Iperf 2.x is: http://sourceforge.net/projects/iperf/.

Iperf3 is a new implementation from scratch. It is not backward compatible with Iperf 2.x. The homepage of Iperf3 is: http://code.google.com/p/iperf/.

The objective of this project is to develop a user-friendly network performance test tool with graphical user interface. The GUI of Iperf3-Cygwin-GUI is based on Jperf.
summary: Iperf3-Cygwin-GUI is a GUI frontend for Iperf3
